WEBVTT

01:42.960 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:50.080 --> 01:53.520
Jiaxu, what will you be doing

01:54.000 --> 01:55.080
while I study?

01:56.480 --> 01:57.480
I will

01:57.560 --> 01:58.760
just be sitting here.

02:00.880 --> 02:02.080
You'll just be sitting here?

02:02.720 --> 02:05.160
I want to look at you more.

02:36.200 --> 02:37.360
Is that enough for you?

02:38.200 --> 02:40.320
If you don't leave,
I won't be able to focus.

02:55.200 --> 02:56.640
Can't I stay here

02:59.240 --> 03:01.200
without saying a word?

03:02.760 --> 03:04.720
You said you won't

03:04.800 --> 03:06.240
get in the way of my studies.

03:17.600 --> 03:18.640
All right then.

03:21.320 --> 03:23.040
You're such a cruel girlfriend.

03:25.920 --> 03:27.400
Go ahead and study.

03:34.040 --> 03:35.120
What do you want to eat?

03:35.200 --> 03:36.400
I'll make you something tasty.

03:37.280 --> 03:39.120
Zhizhi has been studying hard.

03:43.920 --> 03:45.520
I'm fine with anything

03:45.600 --> 03:47.400
as long as you make it.

03:49.880 --> 03:50.920
Okay.

03:51.000 --> 03:53.240
Then let me know if you need anything.

03:55.240 --> 03:56.400
Jiaxu.

03:56.480 --> 03:58.880
Why does it feel like
you're taking care of a kid?

03:59.680 --> 04:00.560
That's what I'm doing.

04:01.520 --> 04:02.720
I'm afraid

04:02.800 --> 04:04.640
someone might steal my kiddo.

04:23.080 --> 04:25.080
CHAPTER 18, CAPTIVATED

04:25.160 --> 04:26.720
THE TASTE OF FIRST LOVE

04:44.360 --> 04:45.440
Jiaxu.

04:46.080 --> 04:48.080
I think your cooking is really delicious.

04:49.480 --> 04:50.480
Do you like it?

04:51.520 --> 04:53.080
Not just anyone gets to taste it.

04:53.600 --> 04:54.800
You're the first one.

05:07.600 --> 05:09.200
- Are you full?
- I'm full.

05:12.080 --> 05:13.440
Are you full?

05:14.120 --> 05:15.440
Are you full too?

05:16.160 --> 05:17.800
Give it to me. I'll do the dishes.

05:18.880 --> 05:20.560
Get some rest. I can do the dishes.

05:20.640 --> 05:21.960
Let me help you with something.

05:22.040 --> 05:23.320
You already cooked.

05:23.400 --> 05:24.720
So I'll do the dishes.

05:25.280 --> 05:26.560
You can rest.

05:29.320 --> 05:30.440
Okay.

05:30.520 --> 05:32.280
- I'll bring you the dishes.
- Okay.

05:36.680 --> 05:38.000
Just leave them here.

05:48.200 --> 05:49.360
Here.

06:10.840 --> 06:12.440
Don't you know how to do housework?

06:12.520 --> 06:13.920
Why don't I take over?

06:14.560 --> 06:16.360
I'll learn after doing it a few times.

06:17.120 --> 06:18.480
Why do you need to learn?

06:18.560 --> 06:20.880
I never said you have to learn.

06:21.600 --> 06:23.440
I can't let you do everything yourself

06:23.520 --> 06:24.400
in the future.

06:28.440 --> 06:30.080
I am thinking

06:31.000 --> 06:32.280
too far ahead.

06:32.840 --> 06:33.760
I know.

06:35.760 --> 06:36.720
So after this,

06:37.440 --> 06:39.120
do you want to chat with me

06:39.200 --> 06:40.440
or rest for a while?

06:43.280 --> 06:45.080
I haven't finished studying.

06:45.640 --> 06:46.680
You'll study?

06:47.200 --> 06:48.800
Aren't you sleepy? Take a nap.

06:48.880 --> 06:50.000
I'm not sleepy.

06:52.240 --> 06:54.320
You sure are serious about your studies.

06:57.080 --> 06:58.600
I'm aiming for a scholarship.

07:00.200 --> 07:01.360
Okay.

07:01.440 --> 07:03.120
Zhizhi is the most ambitious.

07:04.120 --> 07:05.560
I'll help you with the dishes.

08:31.240 --> 08:32.600
I'm sleepy.

08:35.000 --> 08:36.880
Why am I so sleepy?

09:08.400 --> 09:09.360
Hello.

09:10.320 --> 09:11.640
It has been a long time.

09:25.240 --> 09:26.600
I'll nap for five minutes.

09:26.680 --> 09:28.120
I should take a five-minute nap.

09:28.680 --> 09:30.000
Five minutes will do.

09:41.800 --> 09:43.040
Do you want water, Zhizhi?

09:43.720 --> 09:44.720
I'm coming in.

10:01.040 --> 10:02.000
Where is she?

10:02.640 --> 10:03.520
Where did she go?

10:13.600 --> 10:14.720
What are you doing?

10:18.680 --> 10:19.520
I am

10:20.160 --> 10:21.040
memorizing vocabulary.

10:21.600 --> 10:23.360
Why are you doing it on the floor?

10:23.920 --> 10:26.080
This is more exciting,
so I won't feel sleepy.

10:27.040 --> 10:28.000
Exciting?

10:48.320 --> 10:49.560
Do you like excitement?

10:53.680 --> 10:55.520
Then let's make it exciting.

11:07.200 --> 11:09.520
Duan Jiaxu, why are you being naughty?

11:12.920 --> 11:14.320
We're already together.

11:14.920 --> 11:16.560
How can it be called naughty?

11:31.480 --> 11:32.760
Tell me.

11:33.400 --> 11:35.240
How did you end up on the floor?

11:38.040 --> 11:39.680
I was studying.

11:40.640 --> 11:43.000
Then I got sleepy and wanted to nap.

11:44.160 --> 11:47.240
But I was adamant earlier about studying.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.160
I…

11:48.800 --> 11:51.080
If you saw me sleeping,

11:51.160 --> 11:54.000
I was afraid you would think
I was ignoring you, so…

11:55.480 --> 11:56.920
I'm not that petty.

11:57.880 --> 11:58.840
Take a nap.

11:58.920 --> 11:59.960
I'll wake you up later.

12:06.040 --> 12:07.040
Lie down.

12:12.080 --> 12:14.720
Well, won't you feel bored?

12:16.600 --> 12:17.760
A little bit.

12:20.800 --> 12:21.760
But

12:23.200 --> 12:25.440
I'm already happy
that you came here to study.

12:29.800 --> 12:31.000
Take your nap now.

12:42.400 --> 12:43.440
What's the matter?

12:45.640 --> 12:46.840
Jiaxu.

12:48.800 --> 12:49.840
It's not

12:50.680 --> 12:52.360
that I don't like you

12:52.440 --> 12:53.800
being like this.

12:54.400 --> 12:56.280
It's because I get nervous

12:56.360 --> 12:57.440
when you get close to me.

12:57.520 --> 12:59.000
I don't know why either.

12:59.680 --> 13:00.520
So…

13:02.320 --> 13:04.000
I just want to tell you

13:04.080 --> 13:05.880
that it's not that I don't like you.

13:14.520 --> 13:15.960
That means you like me.

13:23.440 --> 13:24.520
Well…

13:25.680 --> 13:27.760
I just don't like being too…

13:32.000 --> 13:32.880
I get it.

13:33.880 --> 13:34.960
If so,

13:36.200 --> 13:37.520
we'll see how it goes.

13:41.040 --> 13:42.280
Take your nap.

13:55.640 --> 13:57.000
Call me if you need anything.

14:33.840 --> 14:34.960
You eat it.

14:41.200 --> 14:42.960
Maybe I should have one.

14:45.400 --> 14:46.960
What flavor do you want?

14:47.040 --> 14:48.280
Any flavor will do.

14:49.520 --> 14:50.360
This one then.

15:02.320 --> 15:04.520
Giving candy or holding hands?

15:17.040 --> 15:18.920
Holding hands or holding hands?

15:27.360 --> 15:28.720
Well, holding hands it is.

15:34.640 --> 15:36.840
Why are you asking this so seriously?

15:39.800 --> 15:41.520
Can I hold your hand?

16:31.720 --> 16:32.800
Have you been

16:33.680 --> 16:35.000
applying for internships?

16:38.600 --> 16:40.840
I've sent my resume to several companies,

16:40.920 --> 16:42.640
but I haven't received any replies.

16:43.240 --> 16:45.200
Why do you suddenly want an internship?

16:50.120 --> 16:51.120
Well…

16:53.240 --> 16:54.440
I want to give it a try.

17:02.440 --> 17:03.520
Thank you.

17:13.160 --> 17:14.000
Jiaxu.

17:16.599 --> 17:18.200
When people hold hands,

17:19.119 --> 17:21.440
they either do it when crossing the street

17:21.520 --> 17:23.280
or by accident.

17:23.839 --> 17:25.160
No one would do what you did

17:25.760 --> 17:27.040
and ask to hold hands.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.520
That was so strange.

17:33.240 --> 17:34.440
I chose to do that

17:34.520 --> 17:35.840
because I made you upset

17:35.920 --> 17:37.600
when I kissed you

17:37.680 --> 17:38.760
without asking.

17:38.840 --> 17:40.240
I wasn't upset.

17:43.200 --> 17:44.160
I was

17:46.080 --> 17:47.000
nervous.

17:50.880 --> 17:51.840
I know.

17:52.840 --> 17:53.800
Now,

17:54.640 --> 17:56.280
you suddenly became my girlfriend.

17:57.080 --> 17:58.640
Do you find it hard to get used to?

17:59.440 --> 18:00.440
Not at all.

18:00.520 --> 18:02.000
Don't imagine things.

18:15.120 --> 18:17.080
Have I not told you this?

18:22.240 --> 18:23.640
I really like you.

18:31.960 --> 18:33.200
I do like you a lot.

19:04.440 --> 19:05.280
Me too.

19:07.160 --> 19:08.200
I like you a lot.

19:43.640 --> 19:44.640
DUAN JIAXU

19:44.720 --> 19:46.080
You have to wake up early tomorrow,

19:46.160 --> 19:47.240
so go to bed early.

19:47.840 --> 19:48.720
Good night.

20:11.440 --> 20:12.280
Hello?

20:12.360 --> 20:13.400
Hey, Duan Jiaxu.

20:14.160 --> 20:16.160
I'm going to Yihe
for work again next week.

20:16.240 --> 20:17.960
Treat me to something delicious this time.

20:18.040 --> 20:19.840
Don't give me fried chicken and milk tea.

20:20.400 --> 20:21.720
Okay, no problem.

20:21.800 --> 20:23.560
I'll give you a seafood feast this time.

20:23.640 --> 20:24.720
How about that?

20:25.280 --> 20:26.720
Why are you suddenly so generous?

20:27.520 --> 20:29.840
There must be a reason
for this abnormal behavior.

20:29.920 --> 20:32.600
Buddy, could it be

20:33.880 --> 20:34.960
that you've gotten the girl?

20:37.760 --> 20:38.600
Yes.

20:38.680 --> 20:40.440
Way to go!

20:41.360 --> 20:43.000
You have to thank me for this.

20:43.080 --> 20:44.840
You couldn't have done it without me.

20:44.920 --> 20:46.680
Yes, so you can

20:46.760 --> 20:49.120
order anything you want to eat, okay?

20:52.080 --> 20:52.920
How nice.

20:53.000 --> 20:55.960
That means you might get married
earlier than Sang Yan.

20:56.040 --> 20:57.360
We should rile him up a bit.

20:57.440 --> 20:58.720
I can't stand him anymore.

20:59.640 --> 21:01.080
No, I'm going to do it now.

21:02.800 --> 21:04.400
Hey, what are you doing?

21:04.480 --> 21:05.320
QIAN FEI

21:05.400 --> 21:06.840
Jiaxu has a girlfriend now!

21:06.920 --> 21:07.840
And I made it happen!

21:07.920 --> 21:10.160
I require worshiping applause
and admiration now!

21:10.240 --> 21:11.200
To Sang Yan.

21:18.920 --> 21:20.280
Buddy,

21:20.360 --> 21:22.280
I have to admit something to you.

21:22.360 --> 21:24.080
I haven't been completely honest with you.

21:24.640 --> 21:25.840
What is it?

21:27.080 --> 21:28.760
You know this girl too.

21:30.600 --> 21:31.600
I know her?

21:32.640 --> 21:34.120
You're in Yihe and I'm in Nanwu.

21:34.200 --> 21:35.160
How do I know her?

21:36.360 --> 21:38.320
You didn't meet her in Yihe.

21:38.400 --> 21:39.720
Not in Yihe?

21:40.800 --> 21:43.320
Do we have any juniors who work in Yihe?

21:43.400 --> 21:44.880
I don't recall any.

21:44.960 --> 21:47.000
She's studying at a university in Yihe.

21:52.320 --> 21:53.400
Studying?

21:54.520 --> 21:56.000
Don't tell me

21:56.720 --> 21:57.880
it's Sang Zhi.

22:01.760 --> 22:03.120
Okay, that's all. Bye.

22:03.200 --> 22:04.040
What?

22:06.680 --> 22:07.680
Seriously, man.

22:07.760 --> 22:09.720
I really have to thank you for this.

22:09.800 --> 22:11.040
Why are you thanking me?

22:11.560 --> 22:12.720
Did I help you with anything?

22:12.800 --> 22:14.080
When you first met Sang Zhi,

22:14.160 --> 22:15.880
she was a short 14-year-old kid.

22:15.960 --> 22:16.960
How could you…

22:19.800 --> 22:20.680
Tell me.

22:21.320 --> 22:22.680
Have you told Sang Yan about this?

22:24.400 --> 22:25.600
I haven't told him yet.

22:26.760 --> 22:28.360
When are you planning to tell him?

22:28.440 --> 22:30.800
I plan to go to Nanwu
and tell him in person.

22:32.400 --> 22:33.760
I think it's better

22:34.560 --> 22:36.800
to tell him in person about this.

22:36.880 --> 22:37.960
That's right.

22:38.040 --> 22:39.240
I have to recall that message.

22:39.320 --> 22:40.720
He'll keep asking me if he sees it.

22:41.760 --> 22:42.760
Hey.

22:43.800 --> 22:45.360
Sang Yan is calling me.

22:45.440 --> 22:46.760
Why did you even send that text?

22:47.680 --> 22:48.640
Answer it.

22:48.720 --> 22:51.120
If you don't,
there's no way to explain it.

22:51.200 --> 22:52.760
Listen, I have nothing to do with this.

22:52.840 --> 22:54.440
You need to be honest with him. Bye now.

22:54.520 --> 22:56.520
How about this? Do it with me.

22:56.600 --> 22:57.560
If you're not there,

22:57.640 --> 22:59.880
I really might say the wrong thing.

23:00.640 --> 23:02.800
SANG YAN INVITES YOU TO A GROUP CALL

23:02.880 --> 23:04.440
OTHERS JOINING THE CALL

23:04.520 --> 23:05.960
Hey, Duan Jiaxu.

23:06.040 --> 23:08.160
Did you lose your marbles somewhere

23:08.240 --> 23:10.160
for you to ask Qian Fei
to help you get a girl?

23:11.400 --> 23:12.560
What's wrong with asking me?

23:13.280 --> 23:15.440
No, you should ask me about these things.

23:15.520 --> 23:16.480
How could you go to him?

23:16.560 --> 23:18.200
But then again, I don't go after girls.

23:18.280 --> 23:20.360
Usually, the girls go wild for me.

23:20.440 --> 23:22.640
Qian Fei is an expert at pursuing girls.

23:22.720 --> 23:24.080
Get lost.

23:24.720 --> 23:25.680
Tell me

23:25.760 --> 23:27.920
who the unlucky girl is.

23:32.480 --> 23:33.680
She is indeed pretty unlucky.

23:34.280 --> 23:36.480
But I still need to thank Qian Fei

23:36.560 --> 23:37.560
for his help this time.

23:38.200 --> 23:39.440
What does it have to do with me?

23:39.520 --> 23:40.400
I…

23:40.480 --> 23:42.320
Duan Jiaxu, how could I have helped?

23:42.920 --> 23:44.680
Besides, I didn't pursue my wife.

23:44.760 --> 23:46.040
My wife pursued me.

23:47.000 --> 23:48.520
Did you really not help him with it?

23:49.440 --> 23:51.120
Qian Fei, why are you so worked up?

23:51.200 --> 23:52.880
Am I?

23:52.960 --> 23:54.880
Why would I be? I don't know anything.

23:56.000 --> 23:58.080
Qian Fei, you're acting a bit strange.

23:58.160 --> 24:00.040
You could brag about this for three years,

24:00.120 --> 24:01.640
but you're actually denying it.

24:02.440 --> 24:04.280
Maybe I've become mature tonight.

24:04.360 --> 24:05.400
I can't believe you two.

24:05.480 --> 24:07.160
Are you shutting me out? Fine.

24:07.240 --> 24:08.440
Sang Yan.

24:08.920 --> 24:10.400
I'll be back in Nanwu in a while.

24:10.480 --> 24:11.480
I'll tell you in person.

24:11.560 --> 24:13.880
Okay. The little demon
will be on summer break too.

24:13.960 --> 24:16.200
You two must help me cart her home, okay?

24:17.680 --> 24:18.840
Okay.

24:19.520 --> 24:20.680
Qian Fei!

24:20.760 --> 24:22.600
That's my wife. I have to go now. Bye.

24:22.680 --> 24:23.680
This…

24:25.960 --> 24:27.760
What was that?

24:36.000 --> 24:37.160
I was in the shower,

24:37.240 --> 24:38.600
so I didn't see your text.

24:38.680 --> 24:39.520
SANG ZHI

24:39.600 --> 24:40.920
I'm going to bed now.

24:41.000 --> 24:41.840
Good night.

24:45.120 --> 24:46.080
Good night.

25:01.200 --> 25:02.320
Is it recording?

25:03.520 --> 25:04.920
Don't be so nervous.

25:05.000 --> 25:05.840
Relax a bit.

25:05.920 --> 25:08.480
Just treat it like a normal chat.

25:08.560 --> 25:10.960
I'll be editing these materials,

25:11.040 --> 25:12.320
so don't worry.

25:12.400 --> 25:13.240
Okay.

25:14.440 --> 25:15.600
Let's get started.

25:17.920 --> 25:20.200
What qualities do you think

25:20.280 --> 25:22.400
an athlete needs to possess?

25:23.880 --> 25:26.720
I guess it's perseverance and tenacity.

25:26.800 --> 25:28.960
Every time we face any difficulties

25:29.040 --> 25:30.360
in a competition,

25:30.440 --> 25:32.160
we must grit our teeth and persist.

25:32.240 --> 25:33.280
Every time we fall,

25:33.360 --> 25:34.640
we have to work hard to stand up

25:34.720 --> 25:36.640
and move towards our next goal.

25:37.680 --> 25:38.760
What do you think

25:38.840 --> 25:40.320
is the most difficult thing

25:40.400 --> 25:42.000
in this process?

25:44.040 --> 25:45.800
It should be

25:45.880 --> 25:47.160
when I can't train.

25:47.760 --> 25:50.440
I remember playing basketball
with classmates in 11th grade.

25:50.520 --> 25:52.400
I suffered an impact on the chest

25:52.480 --> 25:53.640
and my ribs were fractured.

25:53.720 --> 25:54.680
The doctor told me

25:54.760 --> 25:56.200
that I had to rest for a long while.

25:56.280 --> 25:57.840
At that time, I kept thinking.

25:57.920 --> 25:59.800
What if I can't play sports anymore?

25:59.880 --> 26:01.480
What else can I do?

26:03.000 --> 26:04.600
So did you come up with anything?

26:06.120 --> 26:07.080
No.

26:07.560 --> 26:08.920
I only know

26:09.960 --> 26:11.640
that doing sports is what I love the most.

26:13.040 --> 26:14.520
So for sports,

26:14.600 --> 26:16.520
I must cherish my body more

26:16.600 --> 26:17.920
and work hard in my training

26:18.000 --> 26:19.640
to prepare for the next competition.

26:20.680 --> 26:22.160
Actually,

26:22.240 --> 26:23.920
that is the life of an athlete.

26:24.000 --> 26:26.080
Being devoted to something you love.

26:30.680 --> 26:32.560
It's pretty boring, isn't it?

26:33.960 --> 26:35.040
Not at all.

26:35.120 --> 26:37.160
I completely understand your feelings

26:37.960 --> 26:39.800
about being devoted to something you love.

26:48.200 --> 26:49.440
TERM PAPER

26:49.520 --> 26:51.840
"At the beginning
of an intimate relationship,

26:51.920 --> 26:53.960
both of them are all smiles

26:54.040 --> 26:55.280
and full of happiness.

26:55.360 --> 26:57.320
When they gaze into each other's eyes,

26:57.400 --> 26:59.680
there is always love in their eyes.

27:00.880 --> 27:02.520
But once the dream starts to shatter,

27:02.600 --> 27:04.720
the smile turns into a frown,

27:04.800 --> 27:05.960
and the love in their eyes

27:06.040 --> 27:07.800
transforms into anger

27:07.880 --> 27:09.840
or even hatred.

27:11.440 --> 27:13.360
So what exactly happened here?

27:13.440 --> 27:14.560
Why--"

27:14.640 --> 27:16.040
Why aren't you writing your paper?

27:18.680 --> 27:20.360
You scared me.

27:21.880 --> 27:23.960
We told you to write your paper here.

27:24.720 --> 27:26.680
You've only typed two words in two hours.

27:26.760 --> 27:27.720
"Term paper".

27:27.800 --> 27:29.240
Weiwei.

27:29.320 --> 27:30.600
Do you plan to submit nothing?

27:30.680 --> 27:32.320
- Get up.
- I'm really out of ideas!

27:32.400 --> 27:34.280
Tomorrow! I'll go to the library tomorrow.

27:34.360 --> 27:35.360
I'll read extensively.

27:35.440 --> 27:37.080
I'll be able to write once I'm inspired.

27:37.160 --> 27:38.000
Come here.

27:38.680 --> 27:39.760
I'm really going tomorrow.

27:39.840 --> 27:41.240
What time did you go that day?

27:41.320 --> 27:42.360
Were there any seats left?

27:42.440 --> 27:43.320
I'll go tomorrow.

27:44.560 --> 27:45.800
So what time?

27:47.160 --> 27:48.640
Around nine is fine.

27:48.720 --> 27:50.120
There will definitely be seats then.

27:52.200 --> 27:53.600
I didn't go to the library that day.

27:53.680 --> 27:55.520
You didn't?

27:56.000 --> 27:56.840
That's impossible.

27:56.920 --> 27:59.160
You came back very late that day
from studying.

27:59.800 --> 28:01.000
Where did you go that day?

28:02.040 --> 28:03.280
I did study.

28:03.800 --> 28:04.800
But

28:05.840 --> 28:07.200
I wasn't at the library.

28:08.000 --> 28:09.280
Then where were you?

28:12.680 --> 28:14.520
I studied at his place.

28:14.600 --> 28:15.800
- Look at this.
- Hold on.

28:17.080 --> 28:18.440
His place?

28:19.360 --> 28:21.400
Why would you even study at his place

28:21.480 --> 28:23.720
when you two were alone together?

28:26.520 --> 28:27.920
How sweet.

28:30.720 --> 28:31.600
Now tell me.

28:32.920 --> 28:34.040
Did you two kiss?

28:35.000 --> 28:35.960
Weiwei.

28:36.040 --> 28:36.960
Don't tell me.

28:38.120 --> 28:40.240
He made the move, right?

28:40.320 --> 28:41.720
I knew it!

28:41.800 --> 28:43.600
Older guys sure are more experienced.

28:43.680 --> 28:44.840
I want to ask you something.

28:45.400 --> 28:46.600
What is it?

28:47.800 --> 28:49.320
When you and Chen Qiang

28:49.400 --> 28:52.440
have intimate moments,

28:53.120 --> 28:55.720
do you get nervous?

28:56.800 --> 28:58.280
Nervous?

28:59.040 --> 29:01.000
Why would I be nervous?

29:01.080 --> 29:02.280
- True.
- He's the nervous one.

29:02.360 --> 29:04.440
Listen, when we first started dating,

29:04.520 --> 29:06.320
he was afraid to even hold my hand.

29:06.400 --> 29:07.760
It made me so frustrated.

29:08.600 --> 29:09.960
But he's more at ease now.

29:10.040 --> 29:12.520
He even tries to blame me for his farts.

29:13.360 --> 29:14.360
Cute, right?

29:18.120 --> 29:19.040
Wait a minute.

29:20.920 --> 29:22.000
Don't tell me

29:22.080 --> 29:23.360
you were nervous.

29:27.480 --> 29:28.840
I was nervous.

29:30.040 --> 29:30.960
I guess

29:31.520 --> 29:32.680
I might look upset

29:32.760 --> 29:34.360
when I get nervous.

29:34.920 --> 29:36.840
I even explained it
in case he misunderstood.

29:36.920 --> 29:38.920
I told him it wasn't that I disliked it.

29:39.920 --> 29:41.880
But I still think that he…

29:42.840 --> 29:44.840
I don't think he would misunderstand.

29:45.400 --> 29:46.640
But when a couple are together,

29:46.720 --> 29:48.360
they should get along as usual.

29:48.440 --> 29:49.960
There's no need to be so cautious.

29:50.040 --> 29:51.840
But if every little thing

29:51.920 --> 29:53.040
needs an explanation,

29:53.120 --> 29:54.880
it can get annoying over time.

29:54.960 --> 29:56.480
But then again,

29:57.760 --> 29:59.960
are you getting nervous out of habit?

30:01.480 --> 30:02.480
What do you mean?

30:04.400 --> 30:05.560
I mean,

30:06.560 --> 30:08.440
are you always afraid that

30:08.520 --> 30:11.000
he'll find out
that you've liked him for a long time?

30:15.360 --> 30:17.240
There's a possibility.

30:17.880 --> 30:19.680
But you two are together now.

30:19.760 --> 30:21.000
It's common for normal couples

30:21.080 --> 30:23.920
to have some physical contact

30:24.600 --> 30:26.880
when they spend time together.

30:27.360 --> 30:29.040
Besides, Sangsang,

30:29.760 --> 30:33.240
I don't think you're that timid.

30:36.120 --> 30:38.400
I don't know
if you're complimenting or mocking me.

30:38.480 --> 30:40.320
I'm encouraging you.

30:40.400 --> 30:42.280
You should enjoy being in a relationship.

30:42.360 --> 30:44.760
Savor the process of being in love.

30:44.840 --> 30:47.000
Of course, this process

30:47.080 --> 30:48.680
includes physical contact.

30:49.600 --> 30:50.520
Got it?

31:14.280 --> 31:18.400
But I've already reacted that way.

31:18.480 --> 31:19.760
Won't he read into it?

31:21.040 --> 31:22.040
Read into it?

31:23.000 --> 31:24.600
How about this?

31:24.680 --> 31:26.840
You can take the initiative

31:26.920 --> 31:28.560
and show him through your actions

31:28.640 --> 31:30.320
that you don't dislike it.

31:30.400 --> 31:32.240
You actually quite like it.

31:36.040 --> 31:37.840
I think this could work.

31:40.160 --> 31:41.400
We're already dating.

31:42.440 --> 31:44.000
I'm his girlfriend.

31:44.720 --> 31:46.720
So intimate gestures are normal.

31:47.560 --> 31:48.440
That's right.

31:48.520 --> 31:50.320
There's nothing to be nervous about.

31:50.880 --> 31:51.760
Exactly.

32:01.560 --> 32:02.680
Write your paper.

32:05.200 --> 32:06.320
I really can't write.

32:06.400 --> 32:07.760
I'll go to the library tomorrow.

32:07.840 --> 32:10.040
Spare me this time. Please spare me.

32:10.120 --> 32:11.000
Spare me.

32:11.080 --> 32:14.200
Please spare me, Sangsang.

32:36.600 --> 32:37.600
SANG ZHI

32:37.680 --> 32:40.040
Jiaxu, are you working this weekend?

32:40.760 --> 32:42.080
Let's go on a date.

32:54.600 --> 32:56.560
Sure. Anything you want.

32:56.640 --> 32:59.320
DUAN JIAXU

33:15.120 --> 33:16.120
Now we're all set.

33:18.760 --> 33:20.280
Let me fix your laces a bit.

33:21.320 --> 33:23.680
Did you not sleep well?

33:23.760 --> 33:25.400
You look exhausted.

33:27.000 --> 33:27.920
How so?

33:28.600 --> 33:30.720
You just look tired.

33:31.880 --> 33:33.040
I'm fine.

33:33.120 --> 33:34.400
I slept soundly last night.

33:38.000 --> 33:40.000
We don't have to do this.

33:40.600 --> 33:42.120
We can go out for a walk

33:42.200 --> 33:43.880
or find something nice to eat.

33:44.720 --> 33:46.400
I thought you really wanted to do this.

33:47.160 --> 33:48.480
Are you that worried about me?

33:51.320 --> 33:52.920
I haven't done this in a long time.

33:53.000 --> 33:54.640
I've been waiting to show off my skills.

33:56.440 --> 33:58.040
Let me help you with this.

34:04.200 --> 34:05.120
Slow down.

34:07.080 --> 34:08.440
Hold onto the railing.

34:12.199 --> 34:13.840
I want to warn you of something.

34:14.560 --> 34:15.639
What is it?

34:16.360 --> 34:19.040
I plan to kiss you today.

34:26.400 --> 34:27.960
I wasn't planning

34:28.040 --> 34:29.400
to tell you this.

34:29.480 --> 34:31.880
But…

34:32.440 --> 34:34.440
I was afraid you would find it too sudden.

34:34.520 --> 34:36.080
You're not nervous, are you?

34:36.159 --> 34:38.400
I'm okay too.

34:42.400 --> 34:43.400
So…

34:44.320 --> 34:45.760
Are you giving me a heads-up?

34:50.000 --> 34:53.520
If you don't want to do it today or…

34:54.920 --> 34:55.840
I do.

34:59.200 --> 35:01.720
So will you initiate it or should I?

35:08.080 --> 35:09.760
Of course that would be me.

35:20.520 --> 35:21.760
Are you ready?

35:21.840 --> 35:22.680
Yes.

35:23.480 --> 35:24.360
Okay.

35:25.120 --> 35:25.960
Three.

35:26.520 --> 35:27.520
- Two.
- Two.

35:27.600 --> 35:29.080
One.

35:42.640 --> 35:43.560
Come.

35:44.240 --> 35:45.320
Come and get me!

35:51.760 --> 35:53.720
Skate with your left and right feet.

35:53.800 --> 35:54.760
Slide outward.

35:55.400 --> 35:56.560
- Like this?
- Yes, correct.

35:57.120 --> 35:58.240
Okay.

35:59.640 --> 36:00.840
That's it.

36:01.600 --> 36:02.600
You've got it.

36:03.800 --> 36:05.000
I'll teach you something hard.

36:05.080 --> 36:06.240
A figure-eight turn.

36:06.320 --> 36:07.360
Skate backward like this.

36:07.440 --> 36:08.800
It's a bit more challenging.

36:08.880 --> 36:10.440
Move like this, a figure eight.

36:11.480 --> 36:12.440
An eight.

36:13.680 --> 36:15.080
This is harder.

36:19.800 --> 36:20.760
You can do it.

36:21.240 --> 36:22.480
Believe in yourself.

36:23.400 --> 36:24.280
Come to me.

36:32.600 --> 36:33.640
I'll protect you.

36:35.200 --> 36:36.120
Come toward me.

36:36.760 --> 36:37.640
You can do it.

36:41.880 --> 36:42.920
That's it.

36:43.000 --> 36:43.960
Just like that.

36:45.640 --> 36:46.840
You can do this.

36:46.920 --> 36:48.240
Come to me.

36:53.120 --> 36:54.120
Move forward.

37:21.680 --> 37:23.360
I did tell you about this.

37:30.880 --> 37:33.520
I wasn't ready yet.

37:38.520 --> 37:39.880
It doesn't count.

38:31.440 --> 38:32.920
Okay, time is up.

38:33.000 --> 38:34.440
Please stop writing.

38:34.520 --> 38:36.040
Flip your exam papers over.

38:36.120 --> 38:37.880
Take your belongings
and exit the classroom.

38:41.120 --> 38:42.080
Yu Xin.

38:42.840 --> 38:44.640
Let's go. Stop looking.

38:44.720 --> 38:45.680
All right.

38:45.760 --> 38:47.120
- That's great.
- Let's go.

38:51.000 --> 38:52.240
- Where is Wangwang?
- Let's go.

38:52.320 --> 38:53.920
Wangwang, come on.

38:54.640 --> 38:55.960
- What are you reading?
- What is it?

38:56.040 --> 38:57.400
For the last question

38:57.480 --> 38:59.680
about the characteristics
of communication,

38:59.760 --> 39:00.960
how many points did you write?

39:01.040 --> 39:01.880
That one?

39:02.360 --> 39:03.840
It was covered in the mock exam.

39:03.920 --> 39:05.120
- Yes.
- Wait a minute.

39:05.200 --> 39:06.480
Why I didn't see this question?

39:06.560 --> 39:07.520
Where was it?

39:07.600 --> 39:10.040
Timeliness, audience reach,
and wide coverage.

39:10.120 --> 39:11.240
It's okay, Weiwei.

39:11.320 --> 39:12.200
You see,

39:12.280 --> 39:14.040
even if you saw the question,

39:14.120 --> 39:15.400
you wouldn't know the answer.

39:15.480 --> 39:16.960
The result would've been the same,

39:17.040 --> 39:18.280
so it's okay.

39:19.720 --> 39:20.840
Well, that's true.

39:20.920 --> 39:22.600
Forget it. I'll retake it next semester.

39:22.680 --> 39:25.000
But tonight, everyone must celebrate.

39:25.080 --> 39:26.400
Everyone must go. Do you hear me?

39:26.480 --> 39:28.040
- Okay.
- Got it.

39:29.400 --> 39:31.520
Sangsang, did your parents agree

39:31.600 --> 39:32.920
to let you stay to intern in Yihe?

39:33.680 --> 39:34.840
No.

39:34.920 --> 39:36.120
Why not?

39:36.200 --> 39:37.480
Doing an internship is good.

39:37.560 --> 39:38.440
You can start working.

39:38.520 --> 39:40.440
- That's right.
- They do want me to intern.

39:40.520 --> 39:42.640
They just don't want me to do it in Yihe.

39:43.320 --> 39:45.200
They found an internship in Nanwu for me

39:45.280 --> 39:46.280
and want me to go back.

39:47.040 --> 39:48.880
Then go back to Nanwu.

39:51.800 --> 39:54.480
But I still feel that staying in Yihe

39:54.560 --> 39:57.440
may get me more opportunities.

39:57.520 --> 39:59.760
Do you think Yihe
has more job opportunities

39:59.840 --> 40:02.520
or do you just prefer your boyfriend
who is in Yihe?

40:02.600 --> 40:03.960
Stop teasing me.

40:05.600 --> 40:06.800
Hello?

40:12.880 --> 40:13.760
Yes, that's me.

40:15.920 --> 40:16.760
All right.

40:17.400 --> 40:19.000
Okay, I see.

40:21.640 --> 40:23.040
- What is it?
- What's up?

40:25.320 --> 40:26.680
I passed my interview.

40:44.320 --> 40:46.120
I've looked at the file you sent.

40:46.200 --> 40:48.800
I'll work on it some more tonight.

40:49.480 --> 40:50.480
Bye.

40:55.960 --> 40:57.280
Hi. Excuse me.

40:57.360 --> 40:59.320
Can you tell me where I can find a café?

41:00.360 --> 41:02.320
There's a nice café over there.

41:02.400 --> 41:03.640
Over there, right?

41:03.720 --> 41:04.760
Okay.

41:06.360 --> 41:08.120
Can I add you on WeChat?

41:16.200 --> 41:17.160
Sorry.

41:17.240 --> 41:20.360
If my girlfriend finds out,

41:20.920 --> 41:22.000
I'll be dead meat.

41:23.320 --> 41:24.480
Sorry for bothering you.

41:24.560 --> 41:25.400
No problem.

41:41.440 --> 41:42.680
Are you angry?

41:44.400 --> 41:45.280
No.

41:46.240 --> 41:47.080
Drink it.

41:50.440 --> 41:52.040
If not, why won't you look at me?

41:54.880 --> 41:56.200
And you're even pouting.

41:58.920 --> 42:00.920
It's just a WeChat request.
Why would I be angry?

42:02.280 --> 42:03.360
Are you really not angry?

42:05.880 --> 42:06.760
No.

42:06.840 --> 42:07.960
Are you jealous?

42:08.040 --> 42:09.280
No.

42:11.560 --> 42:12.440
Seeing you like this,

42:12.520 --> 42:13.680
I thought you were jealous.

42:17.280 --> 42:18.320
Are you really not jealous?

42:18.400 --> 42:19.400
I am.

42:20.200 --> 42:21.480
Just now,

42:23.760 --> 42:25.320
I saw you flirting with her.

42:26.400 --> 42:27.240
Me?

42:27.960 --> 42:29.760
How did I flirt with her?

42:29.840 --> 42:30.880
You did this.

42:34.200 --> 42:35.120
No.

42:35.200 --> 42:37.360
She asked me

42:37.440 --> 42:38.920
the directions to a café.

42:39.000 --> 42:40.680
So I…

42:41.640 --> 42:42.520
I…

42:43.000 --> 42:45.200
All I did was tell her it's over there.

42:47.080 --> 42:48.800
Couldn't you have told her properly?

42:48.880 --> 42:50.720
Did you have to do this?

42:54.080 --> 42:54.960
I'm not talking to you.

43:03.560 --> 43:04.400
Okay.

43:08.320 --> 43:09.440
Sorry to bother you.

43:09.520 --> 43:10.760
Can I add you on WeChat?

43:10.840 --> 43:13.040
Sorry, I have a boyfriend.

43:13.120 --> 43:14.520
Okay.

43:20.320 --> 43:21.800
This watermelon looks pretty good.

43:22.800 --> 43:25.000
- Let's go.
- What's wrong? Are you angry?

43:26.040 --> 43:26.920
No.

43:27.600 --> 43:28.800
Are you jealous?

43:29.720 --> 43:31.040
How is that possible?

43:31.120 --> 43:32.440
It's just a WeChat request.

43:32.520 --> 43:33.760
Why would I be jealous?

43:36.160 --> 43:38.560
Wait. I didn't give it to him.

43:39.480 --> 43:41.280
But I saw you flirting with him just now.

43:41.360 --> 43:42.680
When did I flirt with him?

43:42.760 --> 43:44.080
He didn't even ask for directions.

43:44.640 --> 43:47.360
You did this to him.

43:47.440 --> 43:48.680
What was that?

43:48.760 --> 43:51.080
I said, "Sorry, I have a boyfriend."

43:51.160 --> 43:53.440
- What do you have?
- A boyfriend.

43:54.920 --> 43:56.000
Present.

43:59.320 --> 44:00.400
Let's go.
